messages.messageBody:
On Mar 22, 2009, at 8:51 AM, Sandra Dodd wrote:

> -=-We didn't win any money, but a clip I sent to America's Funniest
> Home
> Videos is airing this Sunday :-) It's of Sly, one of the horses at
> Partners Therapeutic Riding Center, where I volunteer. It
> should be in the "What's that Sound" segment; I won't spoil it by
> saying more <g> (Sunday night, March 22, on ABC.)-=-
>
> Will it be available online afterwards? It wounds my soul to watch
> that show because of the meanness and derision in so many of the
> videos. I don't like to see people wounded. So maybe Monday could
> you tell us more what it was about, and maybe let us know if the clip
> will be on hulu or youtube or some such? Thanks.
>
> Sandra


I had to sign documents that stated I had not uploaded the video to
any public sites beforehand; I've sent an email to my contact with the
show to ask if it's okay to do so now that it has aired. I'll let you
know :-)

Nancy

messages.messageBody:
-=-We didn't win any money, but a clip I sent to America's Funniest Home
Videos is airing this Sunday :-) It's of Sly, one of the horses at
Partners Therapeutic Riding Center, where I volunteer. It
should be in the "What's that Sound" segment; I won't spoil it by
saying more <g> (Sunday night, March 22, on ABC.)-=-

Will it be available online afterwards? It wounds my soul to watch
that show because of the meanness and derision in so many of the
videos. I don't like to see people wounded. So maybe Monday could
you tell us more what it was about, and maybe let us know if the clip
will be on hulu or youtube or some such? Thanks.

Sandra

[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]

messages.messageBody:
We didn't win any money, but a clip I sent to America's Funniest Home
Videos is airing this Sunday :-) It's of Sly, one of the horses at
Partners Therapeutic Riding Center, where I volunteer. It
should be in the "What's that Sound" segment; I won't spoil it by
saying more <g> (Sunday night, March 22, on ABC.)

Nancy
